public static class AbstractGemFireOperationsSessionRepository.GemFireSession<T extends AbstractGemFireOperationsSessionRepository.GemFireSessionAttributes> extends Object implements Comparable<org.springframework.session.Session>, org.springframework.session.Session
AbstractGemFireOperationsSessionRepository.GemFireSession is a Abstract Data Type (ADT) for a Spring Session that stores and manages Session state in Apache Geode or Pivotal GemFire.
